data.description: Welcome to 9257 SE Olympus. Now is your chance to own one of the premier homes in Zeus Park. This 3 bedroom 3 full bath w/ den/office home boasts a heated salt water pool and spa with the automated iaqualink system controlled from phone/tablet. This well appointed home is situated on an enormous corner lot ( 160 ft frontage) is just steps from Zeus Park. Standing seam metal roof, impact windows, spray foam insulation are just a few of the special features. This home comes with a deeded membership to the private boat ramp directly on the Intracoastal.Make this your full time home / or if desired to be an investment property it comes with a huge book of business. (AirBnb / VRBO)Perfect for families w/ a huge yard and patio/pool area. Furniture negotiable.Professional photos coming soon.
